<seg id=1> Jiang Zhemin emphasized importance of doing a better job on Militia and Reserve duty </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News agency, Beijing, September 1st, by Yuming Gai- The General Secretary of the Political Bureau of the Central Committee, the Chairman of the Military Bureau of the Central Committee, President Jiang Zemin met with some local Militia and representatives of the Reservists today in Zhongnanhai.  He Emphasized that all the departments of local communist committees, government, and military need to pay close attention to doing the better jobs of the militia and reserve duties with the vision of the long term security of the country in mind. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> Jiang Zemin pointed out that militia are soldiers and also ordinary residents.  They are not only an important force for protecting the country's security and keeping the country united, they are also an important force for keeping society steady and enhancing the "two civilization constructions". </seg>
<seg id=4> All the military must provide a guarantee of security to insure the process of reform and steady development in the whole country.  All the military should energetically participate in local economic construction and work hard to enhance the nations prosperity. </seg>
<seg id=5> All the military should enhance the relationships between the government and the military and the relationships between the ordinary residents and the military. </seg>
<seg id=6> To achieve the goal that the military and the nation breath with the same heart and chose the same fate. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> Liu Hauqing, the Vice Chairman of the Military Bureau of the Central Committee of the CPC, and other Committee members Zhong Wangnian, Yu Yongbo, Fu Quanyou also attended the event. </seg>
</p>
